PRE-INSTALL NOTES:

* You may need to install autoconf from gnu.org, as Apple seemingly no longer distributes this with xcode. Pretty painless.
* Make symlinks to clang and clang++ in /usr/local/bin/, for gcc and g++.



Install in this order:

autoconf
automake
libtool

jpeg
libpng

SDL
SDL_image
SDL_net

fftw
libsamplerate
yasm
ffmpeg
jack-audio-connection-kit

Syphon.framework

nasm
libjpeg-turbo

